_sText:
Jon.../: spawn, stages, 1, 3 and 4
Justin.uk: jail, stages, 2 and 5, bonus

This is my first staged map, took just over 1 month to complete.

About the map name, its spelt Genocide, but since its jon and justin, its jenocide.

About the map:

5 Stages
1 Bonus
1 Jail
5 Minute timer

You get a m249 if you complete the map, you also get a smokegrenade with a spirittrail if you complete the bonus :)

Thank you Justin.uk for helping with the map by making stages, 2, 5, bonus, jail and also the custom textures at the spawn.

A big thank you to all the beta testers :)

Thank you the Komaokc for the skybox texture :)
